post_text:
The Mitchell Board of Directors will be considering the adoption of three science textbooks at their regular meeting on September 16th, 2020. The public is invited to review the proposed texts and give written input for the Board to consider prior to voting on this curriculum adoption. The texts are available to review at the school by appointment. Contact Valerie Swagerty at 541-462-3311 to set up an appointment.

The textbooks are:

Glencoe - Chemestry

Glencoe - Earth Science

Glencoe - Physical Science

REMINDERS:

*All prescription medications that need to be given during school, including inhalers carried by students (must be signed by parent and physician).

**All over the counter medications that need to be given during school(must be signed by the parent).

*All medications and cough drops must be supplied by parents.

Please bring any medications and signed notes to the office.
